#Change all the values into numerical type
# Yes --> 1; No --> 0
for i in ['gender', 'Partner', 'Dependents', 'PhoneService', 'MultipleLines',
          'InternetService', 'OnlineSecurity', 'OnlineBackup', 'DeviceProtection',
          'TechSupport', 'StreamingTV', 'StreamingMovies', 'Contract', 
          'PaperlessBilling', 'PaymentMethod', 'Churn']:  
    info[i] = info[i].astype('category')
    
col = info.select_dtypes(['category']).columns
info[col] = info[col].apply(lambda x: x.cat.codes)
info
